    "For example, in contrast to models designed for healthcare professionals to assist in tasks like data documentation, symptom analysis, medication management, and postoperative care, LLMs for patient interaction might be trained with an emphasis on empathy and comfortable dialogue.",
    "Data privacy is another significant area of concern.",
    "Many LLMs, like ChatGPT and Claude, involve sending data to third-party servers opening up the risk of data leakage.",
    "One potential solution lies in locally hosting open-source models or deploying LLMs in private clouds, enabling enhanced control over data storage and access 86.",
    "The lack of interpretability of LLM decision-making is another important area for new work on healthcare applications."
